6 By: Representative Beaty Jr.
7
For An Act To Be Entitled
8
9 AN ACT TO AMEND THE LAW CONCERNING STATUTORY BONDING
10 REQUIREMENTS FOR CONSTRUCTION PROJECTS OF THE STATE
11 HIGHWAY COMMISSION; AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES.
12
